<p>John and Dave are in Las Vegas together for CES and &#8230; for the first time in a long time &#8230; recorded Mac Geek Gab together in the same room. See just how well that works while they answer your questions, share advice and share some fantastic quick tips. Definitely one for the record books, folks. See what happens in Vegas!</p>
